OL,6,FA landslip which led to homes in a
OL,7,Fformer mining community being
OL,8,Fevacuated has been confirmed as coming
OL,9,Ffrom a coal tip.
OL,11,FDozens of people in Cwmtillery,
OL,12,FBlaenau Gwent, were forced from their
OL,13,Fhomes overnight, as mud and water came
OL,14,Fup to their windows following Storm
OL,15,FBert.
OL,17,FThe Welsh Government has now said that
OL,18,FBlaenau Gwent County Borough Council
OL,19,Fconfirmed the landslip was a "singular
OL,20,Fwash-out of a former coal tip in the
OL,21,Farea".
