OL,6,FThe coal tip in the area was category
OL,7,FD, which have the "potential to impact
OL,8,Fpublic safety" and need to be
OL,9,Finspected at least twice a year.
OL,11,FSteve Thomas, leader of Blaenau Gwent
OL,12,Fcouncil, said: "We can confirm that
OL,13,Fthis occurred on the edge of a
OL,14,FCategory D former coal tip. We are
OL,15,Fcontinuing to carry out investigations
OL,16,Fand are working closely with our
OL,17,Fpartners in Welsh Government and the
OL,18,FCoal Authority. We will make a fuller
OL,19,Fstatement in due course.
