OL,9,Fimmediate issues and work towards a
OL,10,Fsafe return for residents."
OL,12,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"We are fully committed to ensuring
OL,14,Four coal tip communities are safe,
OL,15,Fboth now and in the future.
OL,17,F"We are working closely with Blaenau
OL,18,FGwent council and the Coal Authority
OL,19,Fto provide support to the residents
OL,20,Fand to ensure that the area is safe.
